'''后扣带皮层'''（英文：Posterior cingulate cortex）是[[大脑|大脑]][[扣带皮层|扣带皮层]]的尾部，位于[[前扣带皮层|前扣带皮层]]之后<ref name=":4">{{Cite book|chapter=Neuroanatomy, Cingulate Cortex|title=StatPearls|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK537077/|publisher=StatPearls Publishing|date=2021|location=Treasure Island (FL)|pmid=30725762|first=Fareed R.|last=Jumah|first2=Rimal H.|last2=Dossani|access-date=2021-04-04|archive-date=2021-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210221509/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK537077/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。后扣带皮层属于[[边缘叶|边缘叶]]的上部，位于[[布罗德曼分区系统|布罗德曼分区系统]]第23、29、30、31分区（其中第29、30分区为[[压后皮层|压后皮层]]）<ref name=":4" /><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Posterior Cingulate - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/posterior-cingulate|accessdate=2021-04-03|work=|publisher=Science Direct|language=en|archive-date=2021-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210629192009/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/posterior-cingulate|dead-url=no}}</ref>。后扣带皮层是[[預設模式網路|预设模式网络]]中的一个中心结，能与脑部不同网络同时进行信息交流，参与各种脑部功能<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Echoes of the Brain within the Posterior Cingulate Cortex|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6621313/|last=Leech|first=Robert|last2=Braga|first2=Rodrigo|date=2012-01-04|journal=The Journal of Neuroscience|issue=1|doi=10.1523/JNEUROSCI.3689-11.2012|volume=32|pages=215–222|issn=0270-6474|pmc=6621313|pmid=22219283|last3=Sharp|first3=David J.}}</ref>。许多人体[[麻醉|麻醉]]状态及植物状态（[[昏迷|昏迷]]）研究显示，后扣带皮层与[[楔前叶|楔前叶]]可能是人类[[意识|意识]]的神经基质<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Disruption of posteromedial large-scale neural communication predicts recovery from coma|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4676759/|last=Silva|first=Stein|last2=de Pasquale|first2=Francesco|date=2015-12-08|journal=Neurology|issue=23|doi=10.1212/WNL.0000000000002196|volume=85|pages=2036–2044|issn=0028-3878|pmc=4676759|pmid=26561296|last3=Vuillaume|first3=Corine|last4=Riu|first4=Beatrice|last5=Loubinoux|first5=Isabelle|last6=Geeraerts|first6=Thomas|last7=Seguin|first7=Thierry|last8=Bounes|first8=Vincent|last9=Fourcade|first9=Olivier|access-date=2021-04-03|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114193413/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4676759/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|title=Posterior Cingulate, Precuneal & Retrosplenial Cortices: Cytology & Components of the Neural Network Correlates of Consciousness|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2679949/|last=Vogt|first=Brent A.|last2=Laureys|first2=Steven|date=2005|journal=Progress in brain research|doi=10.1016/S0079-6123(05)50015-3|volume=150|pages=205–217|issn=0079-6123|pmc=2679949|pmid=16186025|access-date=2021-04-03|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112002535/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2679949/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Consciousness and Anesthesia|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2743249/|last=Alkire|first=Michael T.|last2=Hudetz|first2=Anthony G.|date=2008-11-07|journal=Science (New York, N.Y.)|issue=5903|doi=10.1126/science.1149213|volume=322|pages=876–880|issn=0036-8075|pmc=2743249|pmid=18988836|last3=Tononi|first3=Giulio|access-date=2021-04-03|archive-date=2021-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210525180228/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2743249/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 结构 ==
{{参见|扣带皮层}}

后扣带皮层位于布罗德曼第23、29、30、31分区，但其中第29、30分区的[[压后皮层|压后皮层]]在功能上常被认为是不同区域<ref name=":4" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Retrosplenial cortex and its role in spatial cognition|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6095108/|last=Mitchell|first=Anna S.|last2=Czajkowski|first2=Rafal|date=2018-03-19|journal=Brain and Neuroscience Advances|doi=10.1177/2398212818757098|volume=2|issn=2398-2128|pmc=6095108|pmid=30221204|last3=Zhang|first3=Ningyu|last4=Jeffery|first4=Kate|last5=Nelson|first5=Andrew J. D.|access-date=2021-08-28|archive-date=2020-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200526215425/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6095108/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。后扣带皮层位于[[前扣带皮层|前扣带皮层]]后方，与[[压后皮层|压后皮层]]、[[楔前叶|楔前叶]]（后扣带皮层的后上方）共同构成了后内侧皮层（posteromedial cortex）的一部分<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2" />。

后扣带皮层属于{{le|旁边缘皮层|Paralimbic cortex}}的一部分，其皮层结构少于6层<ref name=":0" />。后扣带皮层中的{{le|细胞架构|Cytoarchitecture}}不完全一致，前部和背部区域的架构和功能有所不同<ref name=":2" />。

== 功能 ==
后扣带皮层与许多脑部结构均有连接，是脑部[[代谢|代谢]]最旺盛、血液流动最快速的区域之一，超过[[人腦|人脑]]各区域平均水平的40%，但对其一些功能并未有研究共识<ref name=":2">{{Cite journal|title=The role of the posterior cingulate cortex in cognition and disease|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3891440/|last=Leech|first=Robert|last2=Sharp|first2=David J.|date=2014-1|journal=Brain|issue=1|doi=10.1093/brain/awt162|volume=137|pages=12–32|issn=0006-8950|pmc=3891440|pmid=23869106|access-date=2021-04-03|archive-date=2020-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200411162415/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3891440/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在脑部损伤研究中，后扣带皮层被发现与[[空间记忆|空间记忆]]、形态学习（configural learning）等有关<ref name=":3">{{Cite journal|title=Remembering familiar people: the posterior cingulate cortex and autobiographical memory retrieval|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0306452201001087|last=Maddock|first=R. J|last2=Garrett|first2=A. S|date=2001-06-14|journal=Neuroscience|issue=3|doi=10.1016/S0306-4522(01)00108-7|volume=104|pages=667–676|language=en|issn=0306-4522|last3=Buonocore|first3=M. H}}</ref>。此外，在人体成功调取自我记忆（譬如有关家人和朋友的记忆）时，后扣带皮层区十分活跃，但如果调取不成功，则该区域不活跃<ref name=":3" />。由于后扣带皮层与情感的显化联系紧密，故有假设认为，在脑部成功调取自我记忆时，相关记忆中的情感因素是后扣带皮层区高度活跃的原因之一<ref name=":3" />。

后扣带皮层与众多内部控制网络（intrinsic control networks）相连接，是[[預設模式網路|预设模式网络]]的中心结。该网络在注意力不集中（内转）的时候较为活跃（譬如回忆[[情节记忆|情节记忆]]、自我规划、作[[白日夢|白日梦]]等），相反在注意力集中在外部的时候该网络受到抑制（譬如[[工作记忆|工作记忆]]、[[冥想|冥想]]）<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=What about the “Self” is Processed in the Posterior Cingulate Cortex?|url=https://www.frontiersin.org/articles/10.3389/fnhum.2013.00647/full|last=Brewer|first=Judson|last2=Garrison|first2=Kathleen|date=2013|journal=Frontiers in Human Neuroscience|doi=10.3389/fnhum.2013.00647|volume=7|language=En|issn=1662-5161|last3=Whitfield-Gabrieli|first3=Susan|access-date=2021-04-03|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308074738/https://www.frontiersin.org/articles/10.3389/fnhum.2013.00647/full|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 临床 ==
后扣带皮层的结构或功能性异常可能与一系列神经性和精神性疾病有关，包括[[老年痴呆|老年痴呆]]、[[自闭症|自闭症]]、[[多动症|多动症]]、[[重度抑郁|重度抑郁]]、[[创伤性脑损伤|创伤性脑损伤]]、[[焦虑症|焦虑症]]等<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Synaptic Change in the Posterior Cingulate Gyrus in the Progression of Alzheimer’s Disease|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4313125/|last=Scheff|first=Stephen W.|last2=Price|first2=Douglas A.|date=2015|journal=Journal of Alzheimer's disease : JAD|issue=3|doi=10.3233/JAD-141518|volume=43|pages=1073–1090|issn=1387-2877|pmc=4313125|pmid=25147118|last3=Ansari|first3=Mubeen A.|last4=Roberts|first4=Kelly N.|last5=Schmitt|first5=Frederick A.|last6=Ikonomovic|first6=Milos D.|last7=Mufson|first7=Elliott J.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Reduced GABAA receptors and benzodiazepine binding sites in the posterior cingulate cortex and fusiform gyrus in autism|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3020259/|last=Oblak|first=Adrian L.|last2=Gibbs|first2=Terrell T.|date=2011-03-22|journal=Brain research|doi=10.1016/j.brainres.2010.09.021|volume=1380|pages=218–228|issn=0006-8993|pmc=3020259|pmid=20858465|last3=Blatt|first3=Gene J.|access-date=2021-04-03|archive-date=2021-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210525181231/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3020259/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

